         <pb facs="loc.00021.001" xml:id="leaf001r" type="recto"/>
         <delSpan rend="hashmark" to="d1" />
         <lg
              >
            <head rend="underline" type="main-authorial">The Sobbing of the Bells—</head>
            <head type="sub">(Midnight Sept: 19-20 1881)—</head>
            <milestone rend="horbar" unit="undeclared"/>
            <l>
               The sobbing of the bells, the sudden death-news<lb/>
               everywhere,<lb/>
            </l>
            <l>The slumberers rouse, the rapport of the people,</l>
            <l>(Full well they know that message in the darkness,</l>
            <l>
               Full well return, respond within their breasts, their<lb/>
               brains, the sad reverberations,)<lb/>
            </l>
            <l>
               The passionate toll and clang—city to city<lb/>
               joining, sounding, passing,<lb/>
            </l>
            <l>Those heart-beats of a Nation in the night.</l>
         </lg>
         <anchor xml:id="d1"/>
         <pb facs="loc.00021.002" xml:id="leaf001v" type="verso"/>
         <div1 type="prose">
            <note type="authorial"
                  place="top">
               <del rend="erasure">
                  <gap reason="deletion, illegible"/>
               </del> new <unclear reason="illegible" resp="#awj" cert="medium">mount</unclear> 
               <del rend="erasure">
                  <gap reason="deletion, illegible"/>
               </del> 
               <del rend="overstrike">permanently</del>
            </note>
            <note type="authorial"
                  rend="circled"
                  place="left">brev leaded</note>
            <note type="authorial"
                  rend="circled"
                  place="right">pp 27.8. 279 &amp; part of 280 &amp; all of 281 leaded brev</note>
            <delSpan rend="hashmark" to="d2" />
            <p>
               <del rend="overstrike">What</del> 
               <del rend="overstrike">If it were</del>
            </p>
            <p>To recover what was <subst>
                  <rdg varSeq="1">
                     <del rend="overstrike">generally</del>
                  </rdg>
                  <rdg varSeq="2"> 
                     <del rend="overstrike">
                        <add rend="unmarked" place="supralinear">distinctively</add>
                     </del>
                  </rdg>
               </subst> said <del rend="overstrike">at the time of</del> 
               <del rend="overstrike">some</del> 
               <add rend="unmarked" place="supralinear">of</add> any important <add rend="insertion" place="supralinear">past</add> event or person—<add rend="insertion" place="supralinear">in its or his own time—</add>what the wise ones had to offer, <add rend="insertion" place="supralinear">or <subst>
                     <rdg varSeq="1">
                        <del rend="overstrike">
                           <orig reg="postulate">posulate</orig>
                        </del>
                     </rdg>
                     <rdg varSeq="2"> 
                        <add rend="insertion" place="supralinear">comment</add>
                     </rdg>
                  </subst> or predict,</add> on the <del rend="overstrike">first</del> appearance of <del rend="overstrike">the</del> 
               <del rend="overstrike">an</del> 
               <add rend="unmarked" place="supralinear">
                  <subst>
                     <rdg varSeq="1">
                        <del rend="overstrike">the</del>
                     </rdg>
                     <rdg varSeq="2"> 
                        <add rend="unmarked" place="supralinear">a</add>
                     </rdg>
                  </subst> new</add> orb above the <del rend="overstrike">eastern</del> horizon—would <add rend="insertion" place="supralinear">it not</add> indeed afford <subst>
                  <rdg varSeq="1">
                     <del rend="overstrike">some of dee lessons and suggestions</del>
                  </rdg>
                  <rdg varSeq="2"> 
                     <add rend="unmarked" place="supralinear">lessons</add>
                  </rdg>
               </subst> of <add rend="insertion" place="supralinear">the</add> deepest, sometimes of <add rend="insertion" place="supralinear">an unquestionably</add> comic, significance?</p>
         </div1>
